<<main_headline>>
<m0>Owner removes boat from Intracoastal<ql>
<m1><ue5><m4>   LINE 1 IS 1.01 PICA(S) SHORT<m2><ql>
<m4>   TOTAL HEAD DEPTH IS .576 INCHES<m2><ql>
